Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.42,0:01:53.26,OPCH,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}涌上心头的 感动
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.18,0:02:03.35,OPCH,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}沐浴着湛蓝的阳光
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.21,0:02:07.71,OPCH,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}你迎风前行的身姿
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.03,0:02:14.39,OPCH,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}让我陶醉时 目光相遇
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.51,0:02:19.25,OPCH,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}我们齐声欢笑
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.10,0:02:26.52,OPCH,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}就像那 小小漩涡
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.39,0:02:33.30,OPCH,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,1000)\an3}无论何时 都想挥动双手的日子
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.18,0:02:37.59,OPCH,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}确实是 曾经
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.98,0:02:43.12,OPCH,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}与你同在的印记
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.87,0:02:47.47,OPCH,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}永远如 小小漩涡
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.88,0:02:57.26,OPCH,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}我们的前方 道路在延伸
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.68,0:03:05.99,OPCH,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}攀上 下一个陡坡后
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.78,0:03:10.75,OPCH,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,1000)}我们再相见吧
